EXAM C — "From Protocol to Principle to Big Picture"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Narrative arc: zoom out in three steps — start from one concrete, modern
Web protocol (WebSub) → generalize to the architectural design principle
it embodies (loose coupling / hard-coding in hypermedia vs. CRUD APIs) →
finish by zooming all the way out to the historical and societal question
of what kind of Web we could have had (Xanadu) and what that means for
